attributes.description: Sunrise across Principal Valley to signify a new light and journey
Red Elves are believed to be descendants of the Ancestral Degens, whose skin was tempered by the fiery forges of the Degen Inferno
This tight-fitting outfit is reserved for night-time missions, as sunlight tends to damage leather. It gives off a particular shine, as if emitting its own light
Long hair worn worn loosely as if unconcerned with worldly matters. White with wisdom and ancient knowledge
Seeking balance in all things, as with their emotions
Elves are a naturally inquisitive lot, always doing their own research, skeptical of tall tales
Dark eyes are better for not drawing attention and capture more detail in the night
Woven by the owner's magic, it imbues a fragment of the Wizard's soul. Yellow represents its creator's ambition
Many elves use eyepatches to attune their vision to darkness. Some say it also improves their luck
